---
title: Crumbed Sichuan Chicken & Fries with Peanuts & Creamy Slaw
description: Wait, did you smell that crumbed chicken? It smells so good and it’s all thanks to the rising star, taste sensation, Sichuan garlic paste.
That’s right, your mouth is watering all because of those irresistible flavours. Alongside a serving of fries, cooking up this dinner will make
you the talk of the town.
